Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.05,0:00:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.95,0:00:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.09,0:00:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.10,0:00:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.41,0:00:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.14,0:00:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.75,0:00:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.79,0:00:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.09,0:01:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.06,0:01:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好崇拜她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.56,0:02:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神不管做什麼都好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.50,0:02:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文武雙全,接下來只剩戀愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.87,0:02:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想談戀愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正中紅心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.19,0:02:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#54 裸體進攻!\N五代招架不住的誘惑作戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.84,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此,“心”這部作品是在描述
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.34,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於主角的“我”偷跑\N超越了友人“K”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.81,0:03:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果逼得“K”自殺的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,八神同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.69,0:03:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假設五代老師是主角“我”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後假設這棟出租公寓的寡婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.47,0:03:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個二十幾歲的絕色美女的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.40,0:03:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩者間的戀愛關係會成立嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太明白妳到底要問什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.61,0:03:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想問的是\N你喜歡那個寡婦嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.52,0:03:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這跟上課內容有什麼關係呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要敷衍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.89,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道五代老師的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太扯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.41,0:04:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被那種小問題弄得手足無措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是搞不懂到底誰才是學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.41,0:04:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.65,0:04:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神同學好像對你很有意思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.85,0:04:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.72,0:04:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管她的外表長得多麼成熟\N畢竟還是個小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論在任何情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.66,0:04:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能輸給你的情慾\N拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不用妳拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,我會謹記於心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一個禮拜\N五代老師就要走了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.65,0:04:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心,好歹我也是班長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.66,0:04:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他獨處的機會,還多得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-再見了\N-拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以目前的清掃工作分配\N怎麼看都很不公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.64,0:05:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想出了一個辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼班長,接下來麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.35,0:05:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.95,0:05:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-老師\N-哦,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先在打掃時分成八組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.20,0:05:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後每一組找一個負責人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.26,0:06:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女…女校一放學就走光啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常都是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-老師\N-什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.21,0:06:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你們還沒走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.82,0:06:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在討論新的清掃工作分配\N因為我是班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.09,0:06:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,早點回去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,已經討論完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,要是出了什麼事\N我可不會輕易放過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.71,0:06:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,你幹嘛逃呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底想怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.35,0:06:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要生氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有生氣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一組的工作內容\N都寫在這本筆記簿裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.85,0:07:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.53,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上完教學實習要回家啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,妳最近好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你很受歡迎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.79,0:08:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學生很喜歡你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.02,0:08:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才怪呢,他們只會消遣我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.16,0:08:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很難說喔,表面上故意消遣你\N搞不好其實是非常的愛慕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.03,0:08:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼妳呢?\N妳曾經喜歡過實習老師嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.74,0:08:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經喜歡一個\N很迷人的實習老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,馬上就忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為兩個禮拜轉眼間就過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.78,0:08:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是,轉眼間就過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.51,0:08:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然會忘記囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.23,0:08:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天回來得好晚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.74,0:09:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟那個叫八神的女孩\N後來怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.62,0:09:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會問這種事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.52,0:09:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,只是那個年紀的女孩\N膽子特別大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想問問看你們的進展如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.26,0:09:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑,那種小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.83,0:09:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只喜歡年紀大的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳能明白就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(我喜歡你)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,竟敢這樣消遣大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.69,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為我不會生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛的激烈告白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都看到了,幹嘛藏起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.43,0:10:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.53,0:10:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不關你的事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?叫得那麼大聲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.27,0:10:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代在寫愛的交換日記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.82,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借看一下,借看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.19,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看一下就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.89,0:10:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借看一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛,小氣鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.74,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了不該說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要拿出老師的威嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我走了\N-路上小…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.75,0:12:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,惣一郎還沒吃飯喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.87,0:12:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是五代忘記帶去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼樣的筆記本呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.99,0:12:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代也真是粗心大意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以上是校方的注意事項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.85,0:13:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有,下午的服裝課\N改在第三家政教室上課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.42,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外,忘記交家長會費的人\N明天一定要帶來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.33,0:13:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找個獨處的機會\N好好訓她一頓才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你\N有什麼事要跟學生們交代的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.44,0:13:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.32,0:13:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代在寫愛的交換日記?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,有問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.89,0:13:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.03,0:13:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在裝什麼嘛\N你就坦率一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.83,0:13:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以囉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.15,0:14:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送妳去學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.52,0:14:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,妳不是要把五代忘記的\N筆記本送去給他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代現在一定很頭痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.93,0:14:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎\N也不是什麼非送去不可的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且筆記本我放在一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係\N來,請上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一點,不然學校要放學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.24,0:14:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也搭個便車回一刻館吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧,管理員\N上車上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.49,0:14:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那我走了\N-好,妳去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.03,0:14:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代一定會很高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.13,0:15:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉,也好,反正很久沒回學校去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你特地送我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.92,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我向五代問好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.23,0:15:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.70,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.91,0:15:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好懷念喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.57,0:16:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.60,0:16:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,那是五代老師公寓的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寡婦來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是來找五代老師的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大膽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太厚臉皮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有看到八神同學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.03,0:16:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.44,0:16:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的一點都沒變耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.75,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.39,0:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎?\N怎麼特地到學校來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代忘了帶東西\N我是送來給他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.40,0:17:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-忘了帶東西?\N-是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.51,0:17:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,那就省事多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.34,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.92,0:17:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳對五代老師究竟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,這樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.31,0:18:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,既然她要用\N年紀大的從容對付我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.95,0:18:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就利用年輕的本錢\N把她解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.59,0:18:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直找不到兩人獨處的機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.47,0:18:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師,快來快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.07,0:18:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-請快點來\N-跟我們來,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.24,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.31,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之跟我們來就對了,快啊快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有奇怪的聲音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.13,0:18:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來沒有什麼異常啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幹什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開門!快開門啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳穿這樣要幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點,要不然我要大叫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.39,0:19:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.59,0:19:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,突然來打擾您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好多年不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.06,0:19:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師一點都沒變\N嚇了我一大跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.53,0:19:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊,千草妳才是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.20,0:19:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,抱歉,應該是音無才對\N以前叫習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.94,0:19:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.68,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到五代是妳的房客啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.68,0:19:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他老師當得還順利嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.75,0:19:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好\N只是有一些學生非常愛慕他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.69,0:19:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手,八神\N不要再鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.36,0:19:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被別人看到的話\N下場會很嚴重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下場會很嚴重的是老師你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.16,0:20:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是為了想困擾老師\N才做這種事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很困擾,非常困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.07,0:20:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳聽我說\N要好好的愛惜自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老掉牙的台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.28,0:20:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘了,是老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.35,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空要再來玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.92,0:20:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢業以後,大家都很少回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.89,0:20:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道還有學生在裡面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.70,0:20:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.54,0:20:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再鬧了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.95,0:20:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我就那麼沒有魅力嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.82,0:21:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼要逃避我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.27,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個公寓的寡婦對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.11,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有必要跟妳說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要敷衍我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止,我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.85,0:21:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.35,0:21:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我話還沒說完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.52,0:21:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.74,0:21:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師\N妳要讓他們鬧到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.31,0:21:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心看到出神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.81,0:21:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.22,0:21:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.52,0:22:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上荻老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.36,0:22:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽我說,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.09,0:22:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.18,0:22:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,沒有被當作色狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.36,0:22:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,幸好我有自制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-五代\N-是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.20,0:22:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子餓不餓?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.97,0:22:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.21,0:22:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方吃點東西再回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.28,0:22:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.81,0:22:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.98,0:23:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼好意思,我請客啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.75,0:23:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-沒關係\N-不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.71,0:23:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,你一定要讓我請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.72,0:23:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.78,0:23:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天真的很想請你吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.99,0:23:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓妳請了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.26,0:23:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們通通給我聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.49,0:23:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算抱著惡作劇好玩的心態\N但是男生會突然產生衝動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.73,0:23:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們平常的言行舉止\N一定要有高中生的自覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.57,0:23:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是八神同學妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.43,0:23:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,我已經深切反省了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.14,0:23:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好,畢竟妳是個班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.97,0:23:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而班長應該更要以身作則\N做全班的榜樣才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.21,0:23:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會為了這點小事就氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!妳要在這裡過夜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.39,0:23:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.36,0:23:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想幹什麼?快把衣服穿上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.93,0:23:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.43,0:23:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.97,0:24:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『睡衣女孩突擊!\N一刻館愛情大混亂』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.57,0:24:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,這下該怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.59,0:24:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.94,0:24:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.66,0:24:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.96,0:24:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.33,0:25:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.24,0:25:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.44,0:25:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.04,0:25:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.28,0:25:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…濡濕而發光
